title: Correct Wall Papers for Year 1918
medium: Machine-printed on paper, with embossed and oatmeal papers
description: Mail order sample book containing wallpaper samples, room illustrations, color illustrations of sidewall and border combinations, and hanging instructions. The catalogue also contains listings for Sanitas, vitrophane, wood moldings and tools. Book contains full range of sidewall papers including embossed, oatmeal papers and independent ceilings.
name: Sample book
